    <p>Celebrity chef restau­rant Adrift by David My­ers has re­opened with new menus. The yak­i­tori menu of­fers more than 30 skewer op­tions and a drinks menu fea­tures over 30 bour­bon and whiskies. Ev­ery Fri­day this month, Adrift will cel­e­brate the launch of its yak­i­tori menu with a pair­ing pro­mo­tion: Guests can en­joy 10 clas­sic skew­ers with a glass of Sun­tory draft beer for $25++ or five spe­cial skew­ers with a glass of Sun Peace Whiskey for $35++.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Adrift by David My­ers, Lobby, Ho­tel Tower 2, Ma­rina Bay Sands, 10 Bayfront Av­enue MRT: Bayfront</p>
    <p>WHEN: All day: 11.30am - 10.30pm TEL: 6688-5657 INFO: www.ma­rina baysands.com/restau­rants/ adrift.html</p>


